This javascript plugin was developed thinking about the workflow behind convering a template to its HTML4/5 counterpart.

The base concept is simple, being able to develop pixel perfect templates.

======

Keys:
Esc: Reset to default position
Alt + Mouse left click: Move background on x axis
Alt + Mouse right click: Move background on y axis
Alt + Both mouse buttons: Move background on x and y axis
Shift + Click: Choose a scope in where to confine your background image
r: Activate rulers (might take a few seconds to load)
Ctrl+g: Activate guides while in ruler view

======

Beta:

This is still in early beta and only works properly on Google Chrome.

======

Examples

You can see it in action here: http://www.joseairosa.com/projetizr